query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `computational_thinking_scores` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  `studentId` int NOT NULL UNIQUE,
  `decomposition` int DEFAULT 0 NOT NULL,
  `patternRecognition` int DEFAULT 0 NOT NULL,
  `abstraction` int DEFAULT 0 NOT NULL,
  `algorithms` int DEFAULT 0 NOT NULL,
  `lastUpdated` timestamp DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
);
